Since Terraform attaches the volume but cannot format it safely 
You must do it manually : 

SSH into the Ec2:

>> lsblk
>> sudo mkfs -t ext4 /dev/xvdf
>> sudo mount /dev/xvdf /mnt/files
>> sudo chown ubuntu:ubuntu /mnt/files

To auto mount after the reboot add the UUID of the block [ blkid ] in to the /etc/fstab
as follows: 

UUID=" " /mnt/files ext4 defaults,nofail  0 2

to test if the mount is good or not use 
sudo mount -a 
